#To use this bot? Nothing's easier !

        1. First, select a Tweet to add to favorites and Retweet, select its identifier 
        (See more -> Integrate the Tweet -> Copy the code in the form "1334542969530183683")

        2. Then paste the identifier into the Last_fav_Tweet.txt file.

        3. Finally launch the Python script.
        
